<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Return &amp; Refund Policy</h1>
  <p class="lead">Last updated <%= year %>. How payments, returns and refunds work on <%= appName %>.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">What you are paying for</h2>
  <p><%= appName %> (operated by <%= appLegalName %>) is a <strong>digital service</strong>. When you launch an election you pay a one-time, per-voter launch fee — shown in full before you pay — for the right to run that election online, including voting links, voting codes, live results and verifiable receipts. Payments are processed securely by <strong>Squad</strong> (GTBank / HabariPay).</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">Digital products are not returnable</h2>
  <p>Because <%= appName %> delivers a digital service that is made available to you immediately, <strong>election launch fees are non-refundable once the election has been opened for voting</strong>. Opening an election delivers the service in full — voting links and codes become live and votes can be cast — so it cannot be "returned". This is standard for digital goods and is made clear here before you pay.</p>
  <p class="help">In short: once you open an election, that purchase is final.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">Before an election is opened</h2>
  <p>If you have paid a launch fee but have <strong>not yet opened</strong> the election, and you believe the charge was made in error or you no longer need it, contact us within <strong>7 days</strong> of payment. We will review your request and, at our discretion, refund the fee less any non-recoverable payment-gateway charges.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">Duplicate or incorrect charges</h2>
  <p>If you were charged more than once for the same election, or charged an amount that does not match the price shown at checkout, we will refund the difference in full. Email us with your payment reference and we will resolve it promptly.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">How to request a refund</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@torama.money">support@torama.money</a> from the address on your account, including your <strong>payment reference</strong> (it starts with <code>vote-</code>) and the election name. Approved refunds are returned by Squad to your original payment method, typically within 5–10 business days depending on your bank.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">Free-tier elections</h2>
  <p>Small elections within the free voter tier carry no launch fee, so there is nothing to refund. You can create and explore the platform for free before deciding to launch a paid election.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2 class="h3">Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about a payment or this policy? Email <a href="mailto:support@torama.money">support@torama.money</a> or call <a href="tel:+2347076096506">0707 609 6506</a>.</p>
</section>

<p class="help" style="text-align:center;">This summary is provided for transparency and is not legal advice. Have it reviewed by counsel before commercial launch.</p>
<%- include('../partials/foot') %>
